data.title: Emma Heming Willis
data.meta_description: Emma Heming Willis. Actress: R.E.D. 2 - Noch Älter. Härter. Besser.. Emma Heming Willis was born on 18 June 1978 in Malta. She is an actress and producer, known for R.E.D. 2 - Noch Älter. Härter. Besser. (2013), Verführung einer Fremden (2007) and The Comebacks (2007). She has been married to Bruce Willis since 27 March 2009. They have two children.
